title: GET_NTH_CLOSEST_VEHICLE_NODE_ID_WITH_HEADING
content:
0x6448050E9C2A72070xC1AEB88D// GetNthClosestVehicleNodeIdWithHeading
int GET_NTH_CLOSEST_VEHICLE_NODE_ID_WITH_HEADING(float x, float y, float z, int nthClosest, Vector3* outPosition, float* outHeading, int nodeFlags, float zMeasureMult, float zTolerance);Parameters:x: X coordinatey: Y coordinatez: Z coordinatenthClosest: The index of the node to returnoutPosition: Pointer to the found nodes coordsoutHeading: Pointer to the found nodes headingnodeFlags: Node flags, see GET_CLOSEST_VEHICLE_NODEzMeasureMult: How strongly the difference in the Z direction should be weightedzTolerance: How far apart the Z coords have to be before zMeasureMult kicks inReturns: Returns the nth closest vehicle nodes id with its heading.
